{
  "stem": "9168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then one of my favorite judges on the Detroit bench, Robert Toms, applied as a judge and was accepted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And an attorney I knew, Murphy, George Murphy, who was the retainer for the University of Michigan attorney applied and was accepted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had our own little-- I could see a-- a Michigan contingent going, and I was going to be the last one because I wasn't old enough.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all, because we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I-- Michigan at that time was a non-capital punishment state.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So here was this great judge, Robert Toms, going from that state to a situation in Germany-- which was interesting, talking to him about it afterwards-- where he had absolutely no problem with verdicts-- sentences of death.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Orientation?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Orders were cut, and I was assigned to the Office of Chief of Council for War Crimes, Nuremberg, Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- and I received those orders at the end of October in 1946, which was over a year after I had originally-- even after I became 21, it took that long, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had the next group of reporters to get, because many of those-- most of them who reported the major Nazi leaders trial, Goering's trial, did not stay on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some did, to report the 12 subsequent proceedings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Civilian employee of the War Department, subject to the military and all that goes with it, including court's martial-- or court martial.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I received my orders.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I packed my mother's trunk with clothes that I would-- I mean, as many clothes as I could get, and other-- anything that you would pack to go on a trip for a year.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
